	<h1 class="title">大英博物馆“复活”木乃伊</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/12/small/12.JPG?1399408627" alt="">
